quran[18{c,v,t}:
68,43,Khaashi'atan absaaruhum tarhaquhum zillatunw wa qad kaanoo yud'awna ilassujoodi wa hum saalimoon
68,44,Fazamee wa many yukazzibu bihaazal hadeesi sanastad rijuhum min haisu laa ya'lamoon
68,45,Wa umlee lahum; inna kaidee mateen
68,46,Am tas'aluhum ajran fahum mim maghramim musqaloon
68,47,Am 'indahumul ghaibu fahum yaktuboon
68,48,Fasbir lihkmi rabbika wa laa takun kasaahibil boot; iz naadaa wa huwa makzoom
68,49,Law laaa an tadaara kahoo ni'matum mir rabbihee lanubiza bil'araaa'i wa huwa mazmoom
68,50,Fajtabaahu rabbuhoo faja'alahoo minas saaliheen
68,51,Wa iny-yakaadul lazeena kafaroo la-yuzliqoonaka biabsaarihim lammaa saml'uz-Zikra wa yaqooloona innahoo lamajnoon
68,52,Wa maa huwa illaa zikrul lil'aalameen
69,1,Al haaaqqah
69,2,Mal haaaqqah
69,3,Wa maaa adraaka mal haaaqqah
69,4,Kazzabat samoodu wa 'Aadum bil qaari'ah
69,5,Fa-ammaa Samoodu fauhlikoo bittaaghiyah
69,6,Wa ammaa 'Aadun fa uhlikoo bireehin sarsarin 'aatiyah
69,7,Sakhkharahaa 'alaihim sab'a la yaalinw wa samaaniyata ayyaamin husooman fataral qawma feehaa sar'aa ka annahum a'jaazu nakhlin khaawiyah
69,8,Fahal taraa lahum mim baaqiyah
